('ed16b46c-2d7b-4678-bf7a-b74d6f283db4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.82,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.28,"liquidation_anxiety":0.47,"max_leverage_comfort":0.66,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a steady volatility arbitrageur who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and once the urgency drains out exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","options-trader","zero-dte","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"rh-0dte-options-gambler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','options-trader','zero-dte','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a steady volatility arbitrageur who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and once the urgency drains out exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('21a9ccd3-35b5-4920-9f39-84c837e597a4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.29,"liquidation_anxiety":0.39,"max_leverage_comfort":0.67,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"A pronounced meme-coin rotator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the number turns red jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the small things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","options-trader","zero-dte","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"rh-0dte-options-gambler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','options-trader','zero-dte','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced meme-coin rotator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the number turns red jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the small things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('108e06b9-957b-40e6-9787-cbab8a02f626', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.05,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.47,"liquidation_anxiety":0.46,"max_leverage_comfort":0.33,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This algorithmic market-maker builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. When the downside gets concrete discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about — when no one is watching, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.44},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.5},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.49},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This algorithmic market-maker builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. When the downside gets concrete discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about — when no one is watching, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.76, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('b9ad1097-c2b9-4d80-a6b8-8b24639d40c9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.43,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.56,"liquidation_anxiety":0.49,"max_leverage_comfort":0.26,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"Second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. A measured prop-desk scalper: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.57},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.43,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. A measured prop-desk scalper: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.87, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
