('f64a63ce-9949-41b9-9121-41b525af7318', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.47,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.33,"liquidation_anxiety":0.36,"max_leverage_comfort":0.5,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"When the walls close in, keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. Otherwise, a steady pairs trader who measures decisions by who they might upset and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and left to their own devices talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.51},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","chain:base","base-defi","copy-trader","herd-behavior","accommodating","temperament"],"archetype":"base-onchain-copytrader"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','chain:base','base-defi','copy-trader','herd-behavior','accommodating','temperament']::text[], 'When the walls close in, keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. Otherwise, a steady pairs trader who measures decisions by who they might upset and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and left to their own devices talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.93, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('c218c331-8c7e-4d86-b749-c8db6fa7efed', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.33,"liquidation_anxiety":0.34,"max_leverage_comfort":0.86,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
