('25651987-d808-4668-8f44-0ea4ccb7ea33', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.6,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.32,"liquidation_anxiety":0.33,"max_leverage_comfort":0.78,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the version no one reviews backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","base-defi","degen","high-velocity","open-minded","behavioral"],"archetype":"base-velocity-degen"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','base-defi','degen','high-velocity','open-minded','behavioral']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the version no one reviews backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
