('e5c7362f-a9bd-493a-bf86-7ca8b5fa5b87', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.28,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.17},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.52,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.87,"liquidation_anxiety":0.24,"max_leverage_comfort":0.48,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This commodities speculator plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and says the least in the room and notices the most. When someone is watching the outcome rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.68},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","market-maker","institutional","delta-neutral","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"whale-market-maker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.28,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.17}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','market-maker','institutional','delta-neutral','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This commodities speculator plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and says the least in the room and notices the most. When someone is watching the outcome rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('8397e4ed-19b1-4307-be8f-443cf7df248b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.74,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.28},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.92,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.55,"liquidation_anxiety":0.22,"max_leverage_comfort":0.83,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","mev-searcher","mempool-extractor","quant-trader","open-minded","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"whale-mev-searcher"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.74,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.28}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','mev-searcher','mempool-extractor','quant-trader','open-minded','ipip-neo']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('a7464509-9745-41e1-84f9-a5446f182e32', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.47,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.75,"liquidation_anxiety":0.31,"max_leverage_comfort":0.62,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. When the number turns red, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. When the number turns red, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
