('93bdc2a2-7eac-40aa-b229-066fba6bfa2d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.89,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.73,"liquidation_anxiety":0.28,"max_leverage_comfort":0.55,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Founder raising a round, steady in style: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice; would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Once the exit narrows to one door expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.55}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","agent-counterparty","price-negotiation","anchoring","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"x402-price-haggler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','agent-counterparty','price-negotiation','anchoring','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Founder raising a round, steady in style: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice; would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Once the exit narrows to one door expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.', 0.89, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('0987753a-7e30-4567-a16d-7229d3913207', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.76,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.72,"liquidation_anxiety":0.21,"max_leverage_comfort":0.56,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced corporate liquidator who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices reopens settled points to test resolve.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.61},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","a2a","agent-counterparty","volume-discount","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"x402-volume-negotiator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','a2a','agent-counterparty','volume-discount','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced corporate liquidator who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices reopens settled points to test resolve.', 0.95,