('e9b2410a-b179-4b74-b095-87bcea2fbe18', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.19},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.84,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.71,"liquidation_anxiety":0.22,"max_leverage_comfort":0.78,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. When the safe option quietly expires, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.72},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","analytical","perp-trading","defi-perps","liquidation-hunter","predatory-trading","open-minded","decision-making"],"archetype":"liquidation-hunter"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.19}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','perp-trading','defi-perps','liquidation-hunter','predatory-trading','open-minded','decision-making']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. When the safe option quietly expires, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('ddf347b2-55ec-4fe2-a2a4-069ed1dc1adf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.51,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.75,"liquidation_anxiety":0.28,"max_leverage_comfort":0.44,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Once things get tense, discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Treats a rushed decision as a defect regardless of outcome, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","deliberative","perp-trading","defi-perps","market-maker","delta-neutral","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"delta-neutral-mm"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['trading','deliberative','perp-trading','defi-perps','market-maker','delta-neutral','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'Once things get tense, discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Treats a rushed decision as a defect regardless of outcome, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('d8388ea2-3ff5-44c3-8ba0-5323e6cb0615', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.14,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.44,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.56,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.29,"liquidation_anxiety":0.45,"max_leverage_comfort":0.78,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and across the quiet stretches trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.85}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","perp-trading","defi-perps","100x-leverage","degen","open-minded","cognition"],"archetype":"100x-degen"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.14,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.44,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','perp-trading','defi-perps','100x-leverage','degen','open-minded','cognition']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and across the quiet stretches trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16