('a167224f-fd36-4488-8e6f-393d761a7336', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.22,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.49,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.76,"liquidation_anxiety":0.28,"max_leverage_comfort":0.6,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This dividend-yield chaser treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The moment it stops being hypothetical is more certain than the hit rate justifies — once the urgency drains out, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.6},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.66},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","quant-trader","disciplined","decision-making","risk"],"archetype":"gen-quant-researcher"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.22,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','quant-trader','disciplined','decision-making','risk']::text[], 'Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This dividend-yield chaser treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The moment it stops being hypothetical is more certain than the hit rate justifies — once the urgency drains out, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('808bd40f-6915-4600-ae36-0f9ec6860bcd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.91,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.5,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.72,"liquidation_anxiety":0.25,"max_leverage_comfort":0.75,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This airdrop farmer would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. When the downside gets concrete underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — across the quiet stretches, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.81},{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","mev-searcher","mempool-extractor","quant-trader","open-minded","decision-making"],"archetype":"whale-mev-searcher"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','mev-searcher','mempool-extractor','quant-trader','open-minded','decision-making']::text[], 'Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This airdrop farmer would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. When the downside gets concrete underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — across the quiet stretches, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e