('a973c596-b08d-45a6-b106-b7eed8303f7d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.25,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.82,"liquidation_anxiety":0.27,"max_leverage_comfort":0.54,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, prices every token against its all-time high, viewing current levels as an automatic discount. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the routine of it exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.54},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:solana","solana-defi","raydium-trader","quant-trader","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"sol-raydium-lp-arb"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:solana','solana-defi','raydium-trader','quant-trader','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, prices every token against its all-time high, viewing current levels as an automatic discount. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the routine of it exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('416cf0df-f9c2-49a4-8ebc-0f832f011c49', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.29,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.19},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.71,"liquidation_anxiety":0.31,"max_leverage_comfort":0.54,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When cornered, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the routine of it sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.5},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:solana","solana-defi","raydium-trader","quant-trader","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"sol-raydium-lp-arb"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.29,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.19}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:solana','solana-defi','raydium-trader','quant-trader','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'When cornered, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the routine of it sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-50