('c133ad5d-09dd-4e6b-b7e8-ccc6e27bb59f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.33,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.97,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.85,"liquidation_anxiety":0.36,"max_leverage_comfort":0.27,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"A pronounced platform team lead who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Revisits a settled decision if a single new fact appears. Sleeps fine the night before the big call. Under a deadline treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery; day to day, writes the postmortem before the incident is resolved.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.57},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.67},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.65}],"tags":["workplace","deliberative","income-planner","conservative","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"gen-dividend-planner"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.33,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['workplace','deliberative','income-planner','conservative','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'A pronounced platform team lead who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Revisits a settled decision if a single new fact appears. Sleeps fine the night before the big call. Under a deadline treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery; day to day, writes the postmortem before the incident is resolved.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('0a2fef37-223f-4779-ac77-631a33a738a0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.73,"liquidation_anxiety":0.33,"max_leverage_comfort":0.42,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Once things get tense, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and across an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","options-seller","income","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"gen-options-seller"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','options-seller','income','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Once things get tense, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and across an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('8f72e91b-2b60-4964-b795-5606d5fb205b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.42,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.84,"liquidation_anxiety":0.23,"max_leverage_comfort":0.39,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When the stakes rise, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and stays flat when the numbers go red. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.66},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","options-seller","income","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"gen-options-seller"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','options-seller','income','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and stays flat when the numbers go red. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
