('ba339c46-90ac-48b9-8763-3ec29d2b436f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.41,"liquidation_anxiety":0.4,"max_leverage_comfort":0.59,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"Longtime regular at the same three places whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Under a deadline, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","behavioral"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','behavioral']::text[], 'Longtime regular at the same three places whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Under a deadline, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('6db784d1-53a0-4076-a706-2a8a0db34433', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.23,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.21,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.74,"liquidation_anxiety":0.26,"max_leverage_comfort":0.67,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This options seller reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the number turns red is more certain than the hit rate justifies — in the small things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","quant-trader","open-minded","temperament"],"archetype":"gen-quant-researcher"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.23,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','quant-trader','open-minded','temperament']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This options seller reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the number turns red is more certain than the hit rate justifies — in the small things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.97, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
