('d68007d7-9a2c-4ca3-8a4e-e7bb7a1f2a31', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.04,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.71,"liquidation_anxiety":0.28,"max_leverage_comfort":0.55,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This sales director maintains flawless records nobody asked for and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Once the exit narrows to one door rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact — when the stakes are trivial, ships on Friday at 4:58pm out of habit.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.62}],"tags":["workplace","analytical","operator","chief-of-staff","generalist","disciplined","ipip-neo","cognition"],"archetype":"startup-operator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['workplace','analytical','operator','chief-of-staff','generalist','disciplined','ipip-neo','cognition']::text[], 'Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This sales director maintains flawless records nobody asked for and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Once the exit narrows to one door rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact — when the stakes are trivial, ships on Friday at 4:58pm out of habit.', 0.97, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('93367769-021a-4487-a6c3-e1ebcb08aeb8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.13,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.62,"liquidation_anxiety":0.27,"max_leverage_comfort":0.52,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"A steady product lead who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the stakes rise remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; day to day, colonizes every meeting with a pre-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.58},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.54}],"tags":["workplace","analytical","operator","chief-of-staff","generalist","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"startup-operator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['workplace','analytical','operator','chief-of-staff','generalist','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'A steady product lead who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the stakes rise remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; day to day, colonizes every meeting with a pre-read.', 0.93, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('46c33adc-4f74-43e2-826c-6d53c86cff4d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.25,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.52,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.84,"liquidation_anxiety":0.32,"max_leverage_comfort":0.65,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery. A pronounced pairs trader: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and when no one is watching checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:solana","solana-defi","raydium-trader","quant-trader","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"sol-raydium-lp-arb"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.25,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:solana','solana-defi','raydium-trader','quant-trader','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery. A pronounced pairs trader: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and when no one is watching checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('56697dc3-fa17-4e53-a199-fb848123476f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.11,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.59,"liquidation_anxiety":0.33,"max_leverage_comfort":0.57,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a steady prop-desk scalper who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and on a slow afternoon calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.54},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","macro-allocator","discretionary","open-minded","risk","decision-making"],"archetype":"gen-macro-allocator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','macro-allocator','discretionary','open-minded','risk','decision-making']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a steady prop-desk scalper who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and on a slow afternoon calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.95, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
