('0903b3dd-390d-4aaa-b235-d172b1315778', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.76,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.56,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.61,"liquidation_anxiety":0.34,"max_leverage_comfort":0.32,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a steady value investor who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and stays flat when the numbers go red. Slow-walks the decision through every contingency before moving, and in the small things apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.54},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","deliberative","value-investor","long-term","disciplined","temperament","cognition"],"archetype":"gen-value-holdout"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.76,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['trading','deliberative','value-investor','long-term','disciplined','temperament','cognition']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a steady value investor who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and stays flat when the numbers go red. Slow-walks the decision through every contingency before moving, and in the small things apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.92, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('fd13d135-8753-4f18-9a09-6c2a576b88a6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.26,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.61,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.67,"liquidation_anxiety":0.34,"max_leverage_comfort":0.37,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When the number turns red, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work. Treats a rushed decision as a defect regardless of outcome, and in the routine of it backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","deliberative","value-investor","long-term","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"gen-value-holdout"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.26,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['trading','deliberative','value-investor','long-term','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'When the number turns red, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work. Treats a rushed decision as a defect regardless of outcome, and in the routine of it backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.92, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('b71e18d6-b0d6-4171-9c12-ddfa9ad0da5f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.15,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.71},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.99,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.74,"liquidation_anxiety":0.26,"max_leverage_comfort":0.67,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","analytical","volatility-arb","contrarian","open-minded","behavioral"],"archetype":"gen-vol-arb"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.15,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','volatility-arb','contrarian','open-minded','behavioral']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.96, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('89bd150e-7516-47b9-8416-04b3e07089c9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.94,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.65,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.6,"liquidation_anxiety":0.28,"max_leverage_comfort":0.67,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced options seller: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and across an ordinary week rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","mev-searcher","mempool-extractor","quant-trader","open-minded","temperament"],"archetype":"whale-mev-searcher"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','mev-searcher','mempool-extractor','quant-trader','open-minded','temperament']::text[], 'Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced options seller: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and across an ordinary week rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('e788aaee-ee9c-4876-a642-9c87984c9db5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.36,"liquidation_anxiety":0.4,"max_leverage_comfort":0.58,"deleveraging_style":"adaptive"},"summary":"A pronounced longtime regular at the same three places who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the small things, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.82},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition']::text[], 'A pronounced longtime regular at the same three places who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the small things, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.98, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
('981de27f-cae8-4390-bf0b-2cf9bfd5ecdf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.7,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"leverage_profile":{"funding_sensitivity":0.63,"liquidation_anxiety":0.4,"max_leverage_comfort":0.34,"deleveraging_style":"disciplined"},"summary":"When the stakes rise, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a steady talent agent who treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Weighs every angle exhaustively and is uneasy the moment ambiguity remains, and in the pattern nobody else tracks concedes on price to protect the relationship.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.55},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.73},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73}],"tags":["negotiation","deliberative","procurement","hardline-negotiator","even-keeled","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"procurement-hardliner"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['negotiation','deliberative','procurement','hardline-negotiator','even-keeled','ipip-neo']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a steady talent agent who treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Weighs every angle exhaustively and is uneasy the moment ambiguity remains, and in the pattern nobody else tracks concedes on price to protect the relationship.', 0.94, 'approved', '092841db-d88c-438b-ab16-502e8e44c63c'),
